1.配置编译环境

下载并安装msys2，在msys2中安装所需的编译器

pacman -S gcc make cmake svn base-devel mingw-w64-i686-toolchain


2.安装tinc依赖库

pacman -S libreadline ncurses zlib liblzo2
pacman -S libreadline-devel ncurses-devel zlib-devel liblzo2-devel


3.编译libmyfec

git clone https://github.com/dnetlab/libmyfec.git

cd libmyfec
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -G "MSYS Makefiles"
make
make install DESTDIR=usr/myfec   (确保消除目录名称中的空格，可通过mv移动库的位置来实现或者cp -a拷贝一份)


4.tinc的编译步骤

autoreconf -fsi

./configure  --build=i686-w64-mingw32 --host=i686-w64-mingw32 --with-curses-include=/usr/include/ncurses --with-myfec-include=/usr/myfec/libmyfec/myfec/include --with-myfec-lib=/usr/myfec/libmyfec/lib
(路径是文件安装的路径。)

make  (生成 tincd.exe tinc.exe 即可)




